undsystemLondon-show-projection-teasers.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="詹姆斯·墨菲（James Murphy）与LCD Soundsystem在舞台上进行现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-show-projection-teasers.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-show-projection-teasers-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-show-projection-teasers-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-show-projection-teasers-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-show-projection-teasers-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-show-projection-teasers-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lcd-soundsystem">LCD Soundsystem</a>似乎正在取笑即将举行的伦敦演出，并进行了一系列预测。请参阅下面的帖子。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-listid="622" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lcd-soundsystem-glastonbury-2024-pyramid-review-setlist-photos-3769986"><b>LCD Soundsystem Live on Glastonbury 2024：Balearic Bliss for Somerset Sunset</b></a></li></ul><p>促销活动已在东伦敦的肖尔迪奇（Shoreditch）弹出。其中一个图形被投影到肖尔迪奇大街车站，第二张出现在附近欧元停车场的涂鸦覆盖的墙上。</p><p>预告片<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-murphy">在</a>DFA Records的闪电螺栓官方徽标上方读到：“您在这里（再次）。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-are-teasing-something-in-london-3173275">纽约乐队在2022年的同一地点显示了相同的预测</a>- 减去“（再次）”，不久之前不久， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-announce-anniversary-residency-at-brixton-academy-3175736">宣布在伦敦O2 Academy Brixemy Brixton居住</a>。</p><p>因此，Muphy and Co。将很快确认首都现场现场表演。 LCD Soundsystem于去年夏天<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lcd-soundsystem-glastonbury-2024-pyramid-review-setlist-photos-3769986">在格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury Festival）的主要金字塔舞台</a>上，在去年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-all-points-east-london-uk-tour-line-up-pixies-tickets-3551502">夏天在伦敦举行的所有积分2024年</a>。</p><p>在此处查看预告片的图像： </p><figure id="attachment_3841166" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841166" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841166" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-Shoreditch-projection.jpg" alt="LCD Soundsystem  - 伦敦投影预告片" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-Shoreditch-projection.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-Shoreditch-projection-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-Shoreditch-projection-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-Shoreditch-projection-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-Shoreditch-projection-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-Shoreditch-projection-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841166" class="wp-caption-text"> LCD Soundsystem  - 伦敦投影预告片。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3841167" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841167" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841167" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-Shoreditch-projection-2.jpg" alt="LCD Soundsystem  - 伦敦投影预告片" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-Shoreditch-projection-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-Shoreditch-projection-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-Shoreditch-projection-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-Shoreditch-projection-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-Shoreditch-projection-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/LCDSoundsystemLondon-Shoreditch-projection-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841167" class="wp-caption-text"> LCD Soundsystem  - 伦敦投影预告片。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>去年12月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-announce-winter-2024-nyc-winter-function-residency-buy-tickets-3795250">在纽约结束了他们的“冬季功能”演出</a>后，该小组尚未在2025年进行任何现场表演。但是，他们最近在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-2025-line-up-announced-tickets-3805796">巴塞罗那Primavera Sound</a>的老虎机之前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-announce-2025-us-tour-3831914">宣布了今年春天的美国头条巡回演出</a>，<a href="https://www.welovegreen.fr/music/?lang=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">我们喜欢巴黎的Green</a> 。</p><p>去年年底， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-share-pulsing-new-single-x-ray-eyes-on-streaming-3808595">LCD Soundsystem分享了一张名为“ X射线眼”的新单曲</a>。在有关即将推出的Primavera表演的新闻稿中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-will-release-a-new-album-in-2025-3806010">据透露，该乐队将在2025年发行一张新专辑</a>。</p><p>墨菲后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-murphy-shares-update-on-whats-shaping-up-to-be-a-new-lcd-soundsystem-album-3808727">发布了有关即将到来的唱片进度的更新</a>，写道：“因此有一首新的LCD歌曲，名为&#39;X-Ray Eyes&#39;。这是成为新的LCD Soundsystem专辑的第一首单曲。</p><p> “不要问我什么时候，因为我们仍在努力。但是，发行新音乐真是太好了。”</p><p>主持人继续重申“尚未完成LP”，并补充说：“但是当我们不参加表演时，它越来越接近完成。这就是新闻。您听到的其他任何事情都是胡说八道的猜测。”</p><p> “ X射线眼”标志着LCD的第一本新材料 - 除了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-release-their-first-song-in-five-years-new-body-rhumba-3320310">独立的“新身体Rhumba”，Noah Baumbach的2022年电影<i>White Noise</i></a> - 自2017年复出专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lcd-soundsystem-american-dream-review-2133039-2133039">“ American Dream”</a>以来，该专辑本身结束了七年的休息时间2010年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/lcd-soundsystem-this-is-happening-what-do-you-think-778717">“这正在发生”</a> 。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lcd-soundsystem-glastonbury-2024-pyramid-review-setlist-photos-3769986">对LCD Soundsystem在Glastonbury 2024年的五星级评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>写道：“包装好的金字塔田地彼此紧紧抓住，并伸向天空，因为LCD的10首歌曲Masterclass自然而然地以“所有我的朋友”结束。这首歌和这一刻是<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2025">格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）</a>最好的表现，在制作中的记忆和美好时光仍然到来：&#39;<em>如果太阳升起，我仍然不想错开，那就是我们的记忆使我们站起来的更好</em>。”这就是它的开始。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-seem-to-be-teasing-a-london-gig-with-projections-around-shoreditch-you-are-here-again-3841144">LCD后的声音系统似乎正在嘲笑伦敦演出，周围是肖尔迪奇（Shoreditch）的预测：“您在这里（再次）”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
