2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">搬到东京，这已经使他为法律文件提供了复杂的努力</a>。下一次法院听证会原定于1月29日，已推迟至3月27日。</p><p>坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）在上个月分享了许多有争议的推文，例如<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">称自己为“纳粹”，并撤回了他以前做反犹太言论的道歉</a>。</p><p>他还推广和出售了以可怕的图像为特色的衣服，例如<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-releases-new-song-beauty-and-the-beast-before-stripping-yeezy-site-to-only-sell-swastika-t-shirt-3836729">在毛巾攻击卡西（Cassie）和瓦斯蒂卡（Swastika）的上述CCTV镜头的屏幕截图，以及后者的特技表演，让他的Yeezy.com商店被Shopify关闭。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-has-come-to-the-realisation-that-hes-not-a-nazi-after-reflection-3839623">从那以后，你们“意识到”他在“反思”时“不是纳粹”。</a> </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-slammed-for-selling-copies-of-cassies-hoodie-from-video-of-2016-assault-3836591"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-apologises-for-inexcusable-2016-video-allegedly-showing-him-attacking-ex-cassie-3757559"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p><strong>有关帮助，建议或更多有关在英国性骚扰，攻击和强奸的信息，请访问<a href="https://rapecrisis.org.uk/find-a-centre/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">强奸危机慈善网站</a>。在美国，参观<a href="https://www.rainn.org/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">雷恩</a>。</strong></p></div></div></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-questions-if-cassie-extorted-diddy-with-sexual-assault-case-3840235">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）的邮政询问卡西（Cassie）是否将“勒索”性侵犯案“勒索”</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
岩石使用莉尔·韦恩（Lil Wayne）的“ tha block很热”，作为他在新奥尔良的WWE入口音乐https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rock-uses-lil-waynes-tha-block-is-is-hot-as-as-his-wwe-trance-music-3840855?u？ tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = rock-uses-uses-use-waynes-tha-tha-block-is-hot-hot-as-as-his-wwe-wwe-wwe-entrance musicKyann-Sian Williams Tue, 25 Feb 2025 11:30:47 +0000 Music NewsNewsTV NewsHip-hopWWE https://www.nme.com/?p=3840855 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dwayne-johnson-lil-wayne-2000-x-1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Dwayne Johnson和Lil Wayne。图片来源：WWE/Getty Images； Erika Goldring/Getty Images。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dwayne-johnson-lil-wayne-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dwayne-johnson-lil-wayne-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dwayne-johnson-lil-wayne-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dwayne-johnson-lil-wayne-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dwayne-johnson-lil-wayne-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dwayne-johnson-lil-wayne-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在此后的新闻发布会上，德韦恩·约翰逊（Dwayne Johnson）说：“这是我向新奥尔良OG展示爱的方式，那就是莉尔·韦恩（Lil Wayne）”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rock-uses-lil-waynes-tha-block-is-hot-as-his-wwe-entrance-music-3840855">岩石的帖子使用Lil Wayne的“ Tha Block很热”，因为他在新奥尔良的WWE入口音乐</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dwayne-johnson-lil-wayne-2000-x-1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Dwayne Johnson和Lil Wayne。图片来源：WWE/Getty Images； Erika Goldring/Getty Images。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dwayne-johnson-lil-wayne-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dwayne-johnson-lil-wayne-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dwayne-johnson-lil-wayne-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dwayne-johnson-lil-wayne-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dwayne-johnson-lil-wayne-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dwayne-johnson-lil-wayne-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/dwayne-johnson">Dwayne“ The Rock” Johnson</a>首次推出了新的新奥尔良风格的入口，该入口在他最近的WWE露面中以<a href="/artists/lil-wayne">Lil Wayne</a>的“ Tha Block”为特色。</p><p>上周五（2月21日）在新奥尔良举行的摔跤手转变的娱乐性polymath出现在<em>WWE：Smackdown</em> 。在他出来之前，他的主食口号响了（ <em>“如果闻起来闻到岩石在做饭……”</em> ），他用莉尔·韦恩（Lil Wayne）1999年的首张单曲“ tha block很热”代替了他的标志性吉姆·约翰斯顿（Jim Johnston）主题，而新奥尔良的图像出现在上面-屏幕。</p><p>在节目后的新闻发布会上，约翰逊解释了为什么他选择重新混合曲目。</p><p>他说：“我一直是莉尔·韦恩（Lil Wayne）的忠实拥护者。” “我一直是<a href="/artists/master-p">P Louisiana Hip-Hop的忠实拥护者，来自P</a> ，<a href="/artists/Juvenile">少年</a>，<a href="/artists/birdman">伯德曼</a>，504。所有这些人。那是我的家伙。我来到迈阿密和南佛罗里达州。这些是我的影响。我爱所有这些家伙。我觉得“我们来到新奥尔良”。 </p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@wwe/video/7474078949757209886" data-video-id="7474078949757209886" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width:605px; min-width:325px;"><section> <a target="_blank" title="@WWE" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@wwe?refer=embed">@WWE</a></p><p>最后一个老板回来了<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/26a1.png" alt="⚡" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/26a1.png" alt="⚡" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/26a1.png" alt="⚡" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/26a1.png" alt="⚡" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a title="WWE" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/wwe?refer=embed">#wwe</a> <a title="therock" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/therock?refer=embed">#therock</a> <a title="拍击下" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/smackdown?refer=embed">#smackdown</a></p><p> <a target="_blank" title="♬原始声音-WWE" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7474078986595797791?refer=embed">♬原始声音 -  WWE</a> </section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> “I wanted to give love to Lil Wayne and I love Kendrick and I love the Super Bowl. I loved his performance so it was my way of showing love to the OG.” -The Rock on dropping his Lil Wayne remix for his entrance on <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/SmackDown?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#SmackDown</a></p><p> <a href="https://t.co/GlVeOFaFRj">pic.twitter.com/GlVeOFaFRj</a></p><p> — Ahmed/The Ears/IG: BigBizTheGod <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f1f8-1f1f4.png" alt="🇸🇴" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> (@big_business_) <a href="https://twitter.com/big_business_/status/1893154051505758221?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 22, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> He continued: “For years, before I would go out and wrestle in these matches, whether here in New Orleans or around the world throughout the United States, I was always listening to all of those guys,” Johnson explained. “I figured, now I&#39;m going to go out, let&#39;s take a moment. I wanted to give love and respect to the OGs.”</p><p> Referring to <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-wayne-discussing-his-super-bowl-dreams-resurfaces-3792246">the controversy over Wayne not being picked to headline the Super Bowl</a> earlier the month, he added: “This is Lil Wayne&#39;s city. I love <a href="/artists/kendrick-lamar">Kendrick [Lamar]</a> , that&#39;s my guy. I love the NFL and I love the Super Bowl. I loved his performance. It was my way of showing love to the OG of New Orleans and that&#39;s Lil Wayne. &#39;Tha Block is Hot&#39;, specifically, I wanted that one.”</p><p> &#39;Tha Block Is Hot&#39; was Wayne&#39;s debut song, released in 1999 as the lead single from his debut studio album of the same name. The track featured his fellow Cash Money Records labelmates and Hot Boyz members BG and Juvenile. When it dropped, the song garnered significant commercial success, making it onto the Billboard Hot 100 and kicking off the illustrious career of the NOLA native.</p><p> Lil Wayne has already performed on WWE programming, rapping the fan-favourite &#39;A Milli&#39; while escorting Jey Uso to his match at last year&#39;s WrestleMania. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Lil Wayne and Jey Uso pump up the WWE Universe: WrestleMania XL Saturday highlights" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zjDlpl2zKE4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Other rappers have involved themselves with the WWE – including <a href="/artists/sexyy-red">Sexyy Red</a> , who <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sexyy-red-could-have-been-a-wwe-superstar-rapping-and-wrestling-are-pretty-much-the-same-3838691">recently said she was offered to wrestle in the promotion</a> but ended up making brief appearances on <em>NXT</em> instead. <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bad-bunny">Bad Bunny</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snoop-dogg">Snoop Dogg</a> have also fought in the squared circle – the former once held the now-defunct 24/7 championship.</p><p> As of last January, Johnson became a part of the wrestling business when he became a member of the board of directors of TKO Group Holdings – the parent company of WWE and UFC. Shortly after, he entered a program with his cousin “Tribal Chief” Roman Reigns – calling himself the “Final Boss” of the legendary Anoa&#39;i wrestling dynasty.</p><p> In other news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/martin-scorsese-dwayne-johnson-team-up-shocks-fans-something-i-never-thought-would-happen-3840148">The Rock is set to star in a new film directed by Martin Scorsese</a> , alongside <a href="/artists/leonardo-dicaprio">Leonardo DiCaprio</a> and <a href="/artists/emily-blunt">Emily Blunt</a> . The movie will explore the Hawaiian mob scene of the 1960s and 70s, focusing on turf wars and resistance against American business interests.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rock-uses-lil-waynes-tha-block-is-hot-as-his-wwe-entrance-music-3840855">The Rock uses Lil Wayne&#39;s &#39;Tha Block Is Hot&#39; as his WWE entrance music in New Orleans</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
